data.meta_description: 064943 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides an overview of projects at Oracle for prospective employees. It discusses Oracle's position as a leading business software and hardware company. It then lists over 50 technology development projects across Oracle's database, middleware, applications, and other areas. The projects cover areas such as database technologies, fusion middleware, applications, and more. The document encourages candidates to browse the various projects and consider opportunities at Oracle's development centers worldwide.
